# context for future sessions / contributors. Previously gitignored on the
# assumption each sandbox had its own local context; the refreshed file
# is purely architectural docs and benefits from versioned history.

# Root-level probe / repro / verify ad-hoc scripts (the canonical
# build scripts under scripts/ are tracked).
/probe-*.mjs
/repro*.mjs
/verify-*.mjs
